</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【評測】SteelSeries Arctis Nova Pro 有線、無線電競耳機，低延遲無線音響傳輸 + 好用實體控制器</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/19/steelseries-arctic-nova-pro/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=steelseries-arctic-nova-pro</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jun 2022 06:15:18 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[評測]]></category><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[遊戲評測]]></category><category><![CDATA[音樂耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arctis Nova Pro]]></category><category><![CDATA[SteelSeries]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1105527</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>遊戲機講求視覺享受之外，愈來愈多朋友想買一部靚聲、清晰話音的電競耳機，在玩恐佈遊戲時增強現場感，在玩 FPS、 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>遊戲機講求視覺享受之外，愈來愈多朋友想買一部靚聲、清晰話音的電競耳機，在玩恐佈遊戲時增強現場感，在玩 FPS、賽車遊戲時認清敵人位置，幫助你出奇制勝。SteelSeries 近日就推出了兩款系列的耳機，包括 Arctis Nova Pro 電競耳機，與 Arctis Nova Pro 電競耳機 (Xbox) 的有線版與無線版，兩者皆附隨特製實體操控盤，音量調整更流暢，更可快速調節網上通話話音與遊戲的混音。以下小編就實際為兩款耳機評測一下。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0014-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105551" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0014-2-694x518.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="518" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0014-2-694x518.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0014-2-1205x900.jpg 1205w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0014-2-768x574.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0014-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲Arctis Nova Pro 電競耳機無線版</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0015-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105552" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0015-1-694x554.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="554" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0015-1-694x554.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0015-1-1128x900.jpg 1128w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0015-1-768x613.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0015-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲Arctis Nova Pro 電競耳機有線版</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0017.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105555" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0017-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0017-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0017-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0017.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>SteelSeries 最新電競耳機系列 Arctis Nova Pro 與 Arctis Nova Pro(Xbox)，包括有線版與無線版本，套裝內含有實體音訊控制器。除了可用 USB Type-C 連接遊戲機／電腦到這個實體控制器之外，玩家可在控制器透過物理旋鈕、按鈕，迅速控制主音量、語音與遊戲音量比例等重要音訊參數、調整均衡器、設定輸入裝置、音量、ChatMix 等，並在控制器表面的 OLED 熒幕掌握這些參數。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0001-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1105529 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0001-1-600x900.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0001-1-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0001-1-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0001-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0001-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0001-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 600px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0004-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105530" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0004-2-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0004-2-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0004-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0004-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Arctis Nova Pro (Xbox) 無線版實體控制器，利用附隨的 USB 線連接遊戲機</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0006-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105533" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0006-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0006-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0006-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0006-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Arctis Nova Pro (Xbox) 無線版實體控制器，左邊的 USB-C 插口支援 Xbox，右手邊的 USB-C 插口支援 PS5/PC/Nintendo Switch 等遊戲機</p><p>Arctic Nova Pro 與 Arctic Nova Pro(Xbox) 兩者最大分別，就是 Arctic Nova Pro 兩個 USB-C 插口都支援 PS5/Nintendo Switch/電腦等裝置，而 Arctic Nova Pro(Xbox) 其中一個 USB-C 插口支援 Xbox 系列遊戲機，而另一個插口支援 PS5/Nintendo Switch/電腦等裝置。如果你家中有 Xbox 遊戲機，就建議買 Arctic Nova Pro (Xbox) 版本。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0023-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105534" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0023-2-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0023-2-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0023-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0023-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲Arctis Nova Pro 有線版</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0025-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0025-1-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0025-1-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0025-1-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0025-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0025-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0025-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a>▲Arctis Nova Pro 有線版</p><p>Arctis Nova Pro 與 Arctis Nova Pro(Xbox) 至於有線同無線的分別，相信也不用多介紹。不過想特別一提，無線版本的 Arctis Nova Pro 與 Arctis Nova Pro(Xbox) 耳機，同時支援 2.4GHz 無線連接，或者 Bluetooth 藍牙連接。代表你除了【耳機－2.4GHz 無線－耳機控制器 (USB)－遊戲機 (USB)】連接之外，亦支援【耳機－藍牙無線－智能手機／平板電腦】連接。同時無線版本都設有 3.5mm 有線插口，可使用隨附的 3.5mm 耳機線有線連接任何裝置。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0030-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0030-1-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0030-1-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0030-1-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0030-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0030-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0030-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Arctis Nova Pro 無線版</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0038.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105537" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0038-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0038-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0038-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0038.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲頭帶有三段調整鬆緊，金屬部份可調整鬆緊度</p><p>Steelseries Arctic Nova Pro 耳機內建有高保真驅動單元，並支援 360 度空間音訊（與 Tempest 3D 音訊兼容）。在遊玩賽車遊戲、FPS 遊戲，可清晰感受到場景內的聲音定位。音效整體調音讓你收聽清晰的效果音，其次給你重份量的低頻重低音效果。</p><p>好多朋友會擔心耳機延遲問題，無線版 Arctic Nova Pro 與 Arctic Nova Pro(Xbox) 其實使用到 USB 連接遊戲機／電腦，已確保音訊有更低延遲，而在控制器中，你可調節到「高速模式」進一步減少延遲。玩音樂遊戲、FPS 遊戲反應會更加好。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0003-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105549" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0003-3-648x580.jpg" alt="" width="648" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0003-3-648x580.jpg 648w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0003-3-768x687.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0003-3.jpg 925w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 648px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0007-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105550" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0007-2-632x580.jpg" alt="" width="632" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0007-2-632x580.jpg 632w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0007-2-768x705.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0007-2.jpg 908w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 632px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032-2-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032-2-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032-2-600x900.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032-2-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p>無線版耳機亦設有主動降噪 ANC 功能，利用兩個耳機中的 4 個咪高風，消除外界噪音。如果家居比較多噪音，例如屋企出面街的車聲，ANC 功能都幫到用家輕減一點。</p><p>而 Windows 玩家可下載 SteelSeries Sonar 音訊軟件，它可控制 10 個音頻頻段的參數，令低頻、中頻、高頻各自擅長的人聲、腳步聲、武器裝備音效能精準地呈現。</p><p>想有更好音質的玩家，可選擇 Arctic Nova Pro 與 Arctic Nova Pro(Xbox) 有線版耳機。兩款耳機附隨的 GameDAC Gen2 的音訊控制器內置有擴音晶片。其 Sabre-Quad-DAC 音訊轉換器與擴音器，提供比電腦音訊輸出更好的音色、聲效清晰度與純淨度，更可把一般音訊提升至最高 96kHz/24bit 水平，提供更清晰細膩的遊戲音訊。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0010-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105531" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0010-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0010-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0010-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0010-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲Arctis Nova Pro 有線版實體控制器，利用附隨的 USB 線連接遊戲機，另可見旁邊有 3.5mm 耳機孔，連接 Arctic Nova Pro 有線版耳機</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105532" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-4-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-4-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲Arctis Nova Pro 有線版實體控制器，左、右兩邊 USB-C 插口都支援 PS5/PC/Nintendo Switch 等遊戲機</p><p>語音通話方面，兩款耳機都搭載了 ClearCast Gen2 降噪咪高風，咪高風在沒用時，可收入耳機裡面，減少佔用空間，使用上也更方便。</p><h2>總結：清晰音質與低延遲並重，實體音量控制器質感優良</h2><p>總括來說，今次測試的有線版、無線版耳機都各有其優點。兩者都能提供清晰而定位準確的音訊輸出，特別適合 FPS 等對聲音特別敏感的遊戲，而無線版更有高速連接模式，可提供更低延遲的音訊輸出。兩者所提供的實體控制器，調節音量旋鈕所用物料都有不錯質感，而雙 USB-C 插口設計，更讓你連接兩部電腦／遊戲機等裝置，再利用實體控制器切換輸入，非常適合擁有多部遊戲機的玩家。想打機有更佳音質享受的朋友，就要留意 Arctis Nova Pro 系列電競耳機。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09394.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105553" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09394-626x580.jpg" alt="" width="626" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09394-626x580.jpg 626w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09394-972x900.jpg 972w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09394-768x711.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/DSC09394.jpg 1188w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 626px" /></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;the